data.description: 2004 Adams Home with over 1700 living square fee. Open floor plan with 3 bedrooms 2 baths. Living room, kitchen with sliding doors that lead to back yard. Master suite with walk in closet off master bath. Laundry Room is in house. Great back yard with plenty room for screened patio and pool. Fresh paint, new appliances, new carpet and vinyl flooring. Close to I95, shopping, restaurant's and beaches. This is a HomePath property.
